| Server | Workers | Req/s | p99 (ms) | p99.99 (ms) |
|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|
| actix_web | 4 | 264,691 | 2.80 | **21.61** ← worst tail |
| hyper | 4 | 221,349 | 2.82 | 3.67 |
| axum | 4 | 201,042 | 2.82 | 3.65 |
